description: Try our easy to follow Pecan Beet Brownies recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Pecan Beet Brownies Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 250g ready to eat baby beetroot, drained

recipeInstructions.text: Heat oven to 160Â°C. Grease and line an 18 x 28cm slice pan with baking paper. Place butter and chocolate into a microwave safe bowl. Microwave on medium for 2 minutes, stirring every 30 seconds until melted and smooth. Stir in sugar and vanilla. Add eggs, one at a time, stirring well between each, until thick and glossy. Set aside.

Process beetroot in a small food processor until as smooth as possible. Stir into chocolate mixture. Sift flour, cocoa and baking powder together. Stir into mixture with choc bits and pecans, reserving 1/4 cup.
Pour into the prepared pan and smooth surface. Scatter reserved pecans over top and press lightly into surface. Bake for 45 minutes or until set. Cool completely in the tin, then cut into squares.
